&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/mhshwom03/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fmhshwom03%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png&h=2dcd081b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續去死撐啦，傻仔同快D用假膠黎掩飾啦傻鳩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1a3a7be8dbe6fb054c42fc52c94565ea379a06","tid":468392,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59add5cdd74486d0cc3b884a72070c7eba3918a9","tid":468392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥絲個傻西靠樓主討伐佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本癲狗從容撚狗，條傻閪卻無招架之力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7684771b9eecda234f604912f8c45c8448993d13","tid":468392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">當肥鳩大隻被拆穿其柒點時，就會以話自己&ldquo;假膠&rdquo;同話對方&ldquo;真心膠&rdquo;來為自己辯護，如下圖:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/huoj9jqeh/Screenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fhuoj9jqeh%2FScreenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png&h=0f10322e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜條傻鳩唔明白一個道理，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係明眼人一睇就知，肥鳩其實就係故事主角既投射</span></span></strong>，例如牠本身又肥又矮，就會引用d主角又肥又矮既故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>所以各位都爭相留下正皮，表示對其恥笑及支持本癲狗的撚狗行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"974cfba9abf6eafd07ad71b0302e53bc4e277be5","