><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由此可見，肥鳩大隻同本癲狗實力縣殊，想借本癲狗上位卻慘敗收場，因而只能作出零星而無力的反抗，反過來誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，其實本癲狗只係從容撚狗，已獲得大家支持</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同時亦證明左，無論肥鳩大隻花盡心機，唸盡辦法想同本癲狗玩，但換黎既結果只有慘敗同被撚，所以永遠活係本癲狗既陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4ef23355172a8e758c66e612095288dde4e15b91","tid":468392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">肥鳩大隻on9邏輯: 原來網上search到自己既身型就等如自己唔係肥佬<br />\n<br />\n小學畢左業先好衝出黎柒啦，係度做小丑娛賓俾本癲狗玩無撚用架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a189724c01b0a0cac305c784262bc12718359bff","tid":468392,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d90035d3d741df01044156aee7cd5b1ca183dca0","tid":468392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥鳩大隻其實傻得好勻秦，所謂既正評得果幾百個讚就沾沾自喜，好似成世未俾人讚過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱，本癲狗一個玩鳩你既post都900幾個正皮啦:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你條傻鳩俾我玩都可以拎黎自豪，將佢演繹成我靠你，咁撚呀Q精神，咁你繼續留係度俾我玩啦，咁你咪俾人玩當贏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依你個on9邏輯，你條肥鳩咪又係靠人打錯字然後抽人水呃正評，你咪靠緊全連登既人上位囉懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-